	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 74. In MRR 2.491, refer also to Wiseman, CQ 14, 1964, 72, and NM 234, no. 199; E. Gabba, Athenaeum 29, 1951, 259; Badian, Studies 60.\n" .
<http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/PostAssertionNote/6888> rdfs:label "Post Assertion Note: #6888" ;
	a dprr:PostAssertionNote ;
	dprr:hasSecondarySourceForNote <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/SecondarySource/4> ;
	dprr:hasNoteType <http://romanrepublic.ac.uk/rdf/entity/NoteType/1> ;
	dprr:hasNoteText "Senator in 74, a juror in the case of Oppianicus who accepted bribes (Cic. Cluent. 71, 75, 78, 98, 103, 127; cf. Schol. Pers. 2.19), and in 70 was expelled from the Senate (Cic. Cluent. 127 and 130)." .
